text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
The material in IRM 22.43.1 is obsolete with the establishment of the Tax Exempt and Government Entities (TE/GE) Communications & Liaison organization.

IRM 22.43.1, Employee Plans Customer Education and Outreach, Obtaining Products and Services from Employee Plans Customer Education and Outreach, dated October 05, 2012, is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
